videos.description: Ty Jerome flings one down low to Mamadi Diakite, who finishes with the game's first bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jerome's great pass sets up Diakite's layup for Virginia) 2019/01/15

videos.headline: Jerome's great pass sets up Diakite's layup for Virginia

videos.description: Ty Jerome knocks down his 2nd triple of the game for Virginia, and stares down the Hokies' bench.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jerome has words for Virginia Tech's bench after 3-pointer) 2019/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jerome has words for Virginia Tech's bench after 3-pointer

videos.description: Ty Jerome draws a double team and is able to locate the open Mamadi Diakite for the Cavaliers' dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jerome makes another great pass to Diakite for Virginia jam) 2019/01/15

videos.headline: Jerome makes another great pass to Diakite for Virginia jam

videos.description: Ty Jerome kicks it out to Kihei Clark, who sinks the trey as the horn sounds to increase the Cavaliers' lead to 22 at halftime.
